Description: Enhanced version of the soils package (WA-Department-of-Agriculture/soils) 
    with dynamic grouping support for California soil health applications. Based on 
    the original soils package by Jadey Ryan et al. Provides soil health data 
    visualization and reporting tools, including dynamic grouping capabilities for 
    treatment comparisons and automated report generation.
